name: Shields Up - Our Nights CDEP
description: A CD Digipak release from Edinburgh's Shields Up - 4 tracks of energetic Hardcore Punk. Highly recommended purchase.

name: Cavalcades - Nothing Worse Than Empty CD/EP
description:
Aberdeen based Screamo/Hardcore band. Handmade artwork and sprayed CDs. Very short run produced (released through Party Wound)

Tracks:
1) April 4th 1968
2) Quiet Voices, Loud Places
3) (a dramatic processing of people and things)
4) Half A Year

www.cavalcadesuk.bandcamp.com to listen in it's entirety.

name: Wolves At Heart 'Write It Down' CD
description: Order our limited run Wolves At Heart EP 'Write It Down' - Our very first release as a label - 5 tracks of exceptionally well written Pop Punk. Digipak CD with full artwork and lyrics. This EP marks a transition in a young and talented Pop Punk band's career. Moving forward with catchy, thoughtful songwriting and professional production. These 5 tracks are well worth your time.

name: !ATTENTION! 7" Four Or Five Ways To Play These Chords
description: !ATTENTION! 7" record: Four Or Five Ways To Play These Chords. We are working with this incredible Toronto Pop Punk band to help distribute this fantastic EP in the UK. Tracks: [A] Four Or Five Ways To Play These Chords Futons Are The Worst Thing To Happen To Poor People Mary Margaret Muise [B] Me, You And Apple Shampoo Super Snack Night Carmichael Drive We only have a limited number of copies, so get in early to avoid disappointment. !ATTENTION! on myspace
